{"tid":1849224,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"料疫情打擊業績 Starbucks關閉中國一半分店","createTime":"2020-01-29T02:42:40.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-29T03:03:19.000Z","uid":28765,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"258b3e9157e4777b5f1e851da6cb43f18274e2db","tid":1849224,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T02:42:40.000Z","msg":"新型冠狀病毒續於中國散播，武漢肺炎肆虐全國，Starbucks宣佈關閉中國一半以上分店，並預期疫情打擊銷售，未能更新2020年業務預測。<br />\n<br />\nStarbucks稱將會密切注視疫情發展，並作適合應對，CEO Kevin Johnson表示仍看好於中國的長期經營前景。此外集團維持2020業務預測，但稱因中國關店太多，未法計算影響，故當中不包括中國部份，但會向股東保持透明度。集團指今年首季表現良好，期內全球同店銷售收益升5%，淨店舖增長6%，意味本年度有一個好的開始。<br />\n<br />\nJohnson向分析員指，因病毒影響供應鏈，Starbucks中國的餐牌被逼調整。<br />\n此外麥當勞、經營中國KFC、小肥羊等的百勝中國，早前仍因應疫情關閉分店。<br />\nStarbucks於中國擁4,292間分店，較2018增長16%。股價週二跌0.15%，報88.6美元，市後時期再跌幅擴大至1.55%，報87.05美元。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/20200129/4XUKDSJDLXTQVE2DSC5YAVSFBI/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2F20200129%2F4XUKDSJDLXTQVE2DSC5YAVSFBI%2F&d=5FuYkWQ3QtYmval6ncx7Jv8K46P7%2BXxs1F7ZCKkfkQw%3D&h=fc0f8495\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2F20200129%2F4XUKDSJDLXTQVE2DSC5YAVSFBI%2F&h=41104d34\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/20200129/4XUKDSJDLXTQVE2DSC5YAVSFBI/</a>"},{"pid":"d6d16d037a78ccc2d6dedf706ede775500c6f7d9","tid":1849224,"uid":343361,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T02:54:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"></span>"},{"pid":"af95e148a97d822e29de0b2a54be2dbb0a156745","tid":1849224,"uid":122275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T03:02:42.000Z","msg":"保平安"},{"pid":"a5beb2b7ab5fa8d95429c7ae544cdceaa762717a","tid":1849224,"uid":25538,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T03:03:19.000Z","msg":"大9獲"}]}